<title>USA: Communications Systems sells Zercom unit.</title>
<headline>Communications Systems sells Zercom unit.</headline>
<dateline>HECTOR, Minn. 1996-11-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>Communications Systems Inc said Tuesday it had completed the sale of the assets of its contract manufacturing subsidiary, Zercom Corp, to Nortech Systems.</p>
<p>Communications Systems received a down payment of $1.5 million and retained Zercom's cash balances and accounts receivable, while extending a five-year note.</p>
<p>Communications Systems designs and manufactures connecting devices and wiring systems for voice, high-speed data and cable television.</p>
<p>-- Chicago Newsdesk 312 408-8787</p>
